    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a highly dependable daily driver for those prioritizing utility. While the engine and transmission are mechanically sound and it handles well on the road, the exterior shows clear signs of age, including some paint oxidation on the hood and minor scuffs on the bumpers. Inside, the cabin is clean but shows typical wear on the driver's seat upholstery and some fading on the dashboard plastics. It\u2019s a solid, honest car that has been well-maintained mechanically despite its cosmetic blemishes.",
      "price": 17500.0,
