    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I am honestly so excited to pass this absolute beauty along to a new home. She\u2019s in incredible, showroom-quality shape\u2014I\u2019ve babied this car from day one and it really shows! Not a single scratch or dent, and it still has that fresh, new-car smell. It drives like a dream and is ready for your next adventure. If you\u2019re looking for something that\u2019s been loved and cared for perfectly, this is the one for you!",
      "price": 43500.0,
