    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 997.2 Carrera S is a benchmark example of the 3.8L DFI flat-six, delivering 385 hp with surgical precision through a traditional 6-speed manual transaxle. The vehicle features a factory-spec PASM (Porsche Active Suspension Management) system and the Sport Chrono Package, ensuring optimal damping and throttle mapping. Mechanically impeccable, the engine exhibits zero bore scoring and maintains perfect compression across all cylinders. The undercarriage is free of oxidation, the bushings remain compliant, and the limited-slip differential operates silently. Every service interval has been documented, including a recent overhaul of the cooling system and a fresh set of N-rated tires, making this a turn-key investment for the discerning purist.",
